00:09:39.800 --> 00:09:41.592 align:middle line:84%
>> So I think the best
way to think about--

00:09:41.592 --> 00:09:47.850 align:middle line:84%
let's think about what we're all
trying to do if we're serious

00:09:47.850 --> 00:09:51.600 align:middle line:84%
