incredible benefits that

00:10:21.090 --> 00:10:24.060 align:middle line:84%
are found in micronutrients,
which are majority found

00:10:24.060 --> 00:10:26.780 align:middle line:84%
in plant food, fruits,
vegetables, nuts, beans, seeds,

00:10:26.780 --> 00:10:28.460 align:middle line:90%
whole grains, whole foods.

00:10:28.460 --> 00:10:32.660 align:middle line:84%
