your mouth to chew,

00:10:32.660 --> 00:10:35.360 align:middle line:84%
either just using your
hands, a knife and fork,

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:40.850 align:middle line:84%
whatever, using a blender,
which will effectively

00:10:40.850 --> 00:10:43.370 align:middle line:84%
outsource the masticating,
the chewing-- you're

00:10:43.370 --> 00:10:45.410 align:middle line:90%
outsourcing it to a machine.

00:10:45.410 --> 00:10:48.577 align:middle line:84%
So you're saving your teeth
and your jaw and the chewing.

00:10:48.577 --> 00:10:49.410 align:middle line:90%
And you blend it up.

00:10:49.410 --> 00:10:50.868 align:middle line:84%
Now, generally to
do that, you need

00:10:50.868 --> 00:10:52.460 align:middle line:90%
to put some liquid in there.

00:10:52.460 --> 00:10:56.267 align:middle line:84%
