nut milk, hopefully,

00:11:00.380 --> 00:11:03.380 align:middle line:84%
that's an almond or a cashew
or some kind of a milk.

00:11:03.380 --> 00:11:05.090 align:middle line:90%
They'll put in a coconut water.

00:11:05.090 --> 00:11:07.580 align:middle line:84%
They'll put in some
kind of liquid.

00:11:07.580 --> 00:11:13.550 align:middle line:84%
So instantly, we are taking
the nutrient density--

00:11:13.550 --> 00:11:19.460 align:middle line:84%
we're actually
deintensifying it.

00:11:19.460 --> 00:11:22.630 align:middle line:84%
We're diluting it, which
is not a bad thing.

00:11:22.630 --> 00:11:25.130 align:middle line:84%
But we just need to be aware
that when you put something in,

00:11:25.130 --> 00:11:28.040 align:middle line:84%
you're diluting
the nutrient value.

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:33.110 align:middle line:84%
