really just consumption of food,

00:11:33.110 --> 00:11:35.630 align:middle line:84%
but somebody else
or something else

00:11:35.630 --> 00:11:39.440 align:middle line:84%
has chewed it for you, in
this case, the blender.

00:11:39.440 --> 00:11:45.273 align:middle line:84%
Juicing is like outsourcing
digestion to a machine.

00:11:45.273 --> 00:11:46.940 align:middle line:84%
Not only are we
outsourcing the chewing,

00:11:46.940 --> 00:11:48.980 align:middle line:84%
we're outsourcing the
function of digestion.

00:11:48.980 --> 00:11:50.550 align:middle line:84%
Because we're saying,
you know what?

00:11:50.550 --> 00:11:55.260 align:middle line:84%
Let's let the blender separate
the fiber from the nutrients.

00:11:55.260 --> 00:11:57.070 align:middle line:90%
So we consume this water.

00:11:57.070 --> 00:11:59.840 align:middle line:84%
