00:12:20.480 --> 00:12:22.610 align:middle line:84%
You didn't fill up
your stomach, so

00:12:22.610 --> 00:12:25.430 align:middle line:84%
to speak, as if you did a
blended smoothie or something.

00:12:25.430 --> 00:12:28.980 align:middle line:84%
